org.gbif.ws.security

Class UserRoles

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.ws.security.UserRoles

  • public class UserRoles
extends Object
    Simple utils class to expose the API user role enumeration also as static strings required by the JSR 250 annotations. Unit tests makes sure these are indeed the same.
